+      "bash scripts/cleanup.sh"
+    ],
+    "result_ttl_days": 30
+  }
+}
+```
+
+---
+
+## Examples
+
+### Example 1: GPU Voice Cloning (Laptop → DevBox)
+
+**1. Laptop creates task:**
+
+```yaml
